Class JsonObjectUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.acs.commons.json.JsonObjectUtil

  • public class JsonObjectUtil
extends Object
    Provide convenience methods to help use GSON JsonObjects similar to the deprecated JSONObject in Sling Json.
